cinvoke: C/Invoke (library for invoking C functions at runtime)
cinvoke: 
cinvoke: C/Invoke is a library for connecting to C libraries at
cinvoke: runtime. This differs from the typical method of interfacing
cinvoke: with C, which involves writing static definitions which are
cinvoke: then compiled to a machine-dependant format. C/Invoke provides
cinvoke: a runtime facility to build descriptions of C functions and
cinvoke: to call them, passing them appropriate data and retrieving
cinvoke: results. C/Invoke provides a central repository of code to handle
cinvoke: the platform-dependant details of marshaling C parameters and
cinvoke: return values.
cinvoke: 
